data.description: Own your own little piece of paradise!!  This beautiful home has been completely remodeled....Brand new kitchen with breakfast bar that is opened to the family room, formal living room with gas fireplace and a formal dining room.  4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Lots of cedar lined closets throughout the house.  Private back yard is fenced in with a above ground pool (4rs), large patio and a hot tub in the gazebo!  Large 2+ car detached garage.
